author: @keepitlight0912
text:
I don’t know where to say this but… Jeongyeon is really helping me be brave. I’m not a Twice fan but her progress in getting back to a healthier body(I’m not saying thin=healthy/ It’s more like a body without the pill-induced swelling and weight gain) and her confidence and love for her work is really inspiring to me. I’ve been on some pretty strong pills for my chronic pain illness and it too has induced a lot of weight changes and a lot of swelling for me. I’m fighting pretty damn hard not to succumb to the health complications and feelings of upset induced by my sudden weight gain and swelling but everyday the fight seems to get a little bit harder. Watching Jeongyeon pop up on my feed just makes my day and her determination really helps me pull through every time. I wish I could communicate my thankfulness and respect to her in some way. You really are a miracle, Jeongyeon. Thank you for performing and being a member of Twice.
She looks great here too. Her outfit is really (finally) nice.
